2 &amp; 1 &amp; 8 &amp; -5 \\
-2 &amp; 2 &amp; -7 &amp; -3 \\
0 &amp; -2 &amp; -4 &amp; 3
\end{array}\right] </m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>Q^{-1}= \left[\begin{array}{cccc}
77 &amp; -22 &amp; 16 &amp; -226 \\
58 &amp; -17 &amp; 12 &amp; -171 \\
-14 &amp; 4 &amp; -3 &amp; 41 \\
20 &amp; -6 &amp; 4 &amp; -59
\end{array}\right] </me>
  </answer>
